These programs are free to use for whatever you want. I wrote them and feel that they're good, clean working 
examples of how to perform these various operations in Pep/8 and such material is sometimes hard to find online
for this application.

Any questions about them feel free to email me.

They are for the Pep/8 assembler and simulator for the textbook Computer Systems by J. Stanley Warford

http://code.google.com/p/pep8-1/